nodes.bodyText: Is it possible for timer_api_service_descriptor to be None as well?

-    if self.process_bundle_descriptor.timer_api_service_descriptor:
+    if self.process_bundle_descriptor.timer_api_service_descriptor.url:

nodes.bodyText: I believe for proto3 all fields are optional and have a default instance thus can't be None.
